import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"base"}}>{`Base`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Following properties are used for all `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`Picker`}</MDXTag>{` Components.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Property`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Type`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`required`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`default`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`markToday`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`boolean`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`false`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`false`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`dateData`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Object`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`false`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`{}`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`initialDate`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Date object`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`false`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`new Date()`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`styles`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`React CSS styles object`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`false`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`{}`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"styles-props"}}>{`styles Props`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`You can customize style with `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`styles`}</MDXTag>{` props. (Thanks to `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://github.com/threepointone/glamor"}}>{`glamor`}</MDXTag>{`!) This props accepts the following keys.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Key`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Description`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`container`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to Root Container`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`header`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to Header`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`table`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to Table`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`yearBox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to container of Year`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`yearText`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to text of Year`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`monthBox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to container of Month`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`monthText`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to text of Month`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`dayBox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to container of week day`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`dayText`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to text of week day`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`dateBox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to container of date`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`dateText`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to text of date`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`selectBox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to container of selected Date`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`eventBox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Applied to container of event`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
